summary.key_stats: Dataset contains sales and customer data with a focus on bakery products and supplier information

insights.description: One country, Japan, dominates the 'country' field in the sales_customers table, accounting for 100% of the values
The top 6 unique products in the sales_transactions table account for 100% of the values, with one product having a unitPrice of 3, which is the only unique value in the unitPrice field
The sales_transactions table has a highly imbalanced distribution of quantities, with 25 unique values, but the majority of rows likely have low quantities, given the low unique ratio of 0.008
All tables have a null ratio of 0.0, indicating no missing values, which suggests high data quality
The 'Asia' continent dominates the 'continent' field in the sales_customers table, accounting for 100% of the values
